@startuml

<style>
note {
    backgroundcolor white
    shadowing 0
    linecolor transparent
}
</style>
note as grid
    |  Line 0  |
    |  Line 1  |
    |  Line 2  |
    |  Line 3  |
    |  Line 4  |
    |  Line 5  |
end note

note as gridline
    |  Line 0  |  Line 1  |  Line 2  |  Line 3  |  Line 4  |  Line 5  |
end note

grid --> gridline
@enduml